node.text:
Fire up a healthy metabolism anytime, anywhere with the Metabolism Duo—back in stock now. Enjoy our Metabolism Super Powder and Metabolism Super Bar together to experience the full-spectrum benefits of a healthy, thriving metabolism, or choose one depending on what your day has in store.

Choose Metabolism Super Powder if you're looking to rev your mornings and ease bloat first thing. Add to coffee, blend into smoothies, or shake vigorously with 8-12 oz water, nut milk, or coconut water. 

Choose Metabolism Super Bar if you're on-the-go and looking to take the power of plants with you. The caffeine-free, functional blend will fuel your workouts and keep up with your packed agenda. 

Questions? Feel free to ask below 👇 in the comments.

node.text:
"Figs" by D.H. Lawrence, 1923

The proper way to eat a fig, in society,
Is to split it in four, holding it by the stump,
And open it, so that it is a glittering, rosy, moist, honied, heavy-petalled four-petalled flower.

Then you throw away the skin
Which is just like a four-sepalled calyx,
After you have taken off the blossom with your lips.

But the vulgar way
Is just to put your mouth to the crack, and take out the flesh in one bite.

Every fruit has its secret.

node.text:
Whip up this smoothie, featuring our Organic Protein + Greens Super Powder, to flush toxins, nourish the gut microbiome, and naturally elevate energy levels. It's simple yet highly effective—we like to think of it as the last smoothie recipe you'll ever need.

½ banana, frozen
1 large handful spinach
1 cup unsweetened plant milk
1 tablespoon nut/seed butter
1 serving of Sakara Organic Protein + Greens Super Powder

Combine all ingredients in a blender and blend until smooth and creamy. Optional: sweeten to taste with a bit of maple syrup or raw honey. Enjoy mindfully and with gratitude ✨
